Installation Instructions
*************************



Basic Installation
==================

	To install coldornot,
	just run "./install.sh".

	This command will compile it, and install the program.



Dependencies
============

	Coldornot doesn't requires any dependencies,
	you will just need gcc to compile it.

	This program should already be installed on your computer,
	if it's not, just look at your distribution's repositories.



Basic Uninstallation
====================

	To uninstall coldornot,
	just run "cd src && sudo make uninstall".

	This command will remove the binary.
